imageGalleryPopupInfoContent.pc_text:
For anonymous users: The list is maintained for current session of design studio only. 

For registered users after login: It maintains the list of all images uploaded by user in several logged-in sessions. User can also attach a high resolution vector source file in allowed formats CDR/PSD/AI/PDF/EPS along with the raster image by clicking on Upload HD button. You can see a right symbol with Upload image button to indicate images who already have the high resolution image uploaded, which can be further replaced is needed. The high resolution source file is sent to the admin once an order is placed for reference.

PLEASE LOG-IN TO MAINTAIN YOUR IMAGE GALLERY AND ATTACH HIGH RESOLUTION SOURCE FILES WITH UPLOADED IMAGES.
